a.n: Agent Binky: Pets of the Universe I (21)

p.k: Undercover of the Night When Binky and Gordon hear a bump in the night, they go to the Room of Many Boxes and meet a new agent, Amelia the bat.
p.d: Binky is an indoor cat who is a member of a secret agency. Teamed with like-minded pet agents, they are on a mission to keep their humans and "space station" safe from "aliens".
